		p Thomas J. Ahrens
		p Seismological Laboratory - California Institute of Technology - Pasadena California 91125
		p Published in 'Methods of Experimental Physics' - Vol 24, Part A, Page 185.
		p Copyright 1987 by Academic Press, Inc.
		p.
			Full text can be viewed at: 
			<a href='http://www.fas.harvard.edu/~planets/sstewart/ahrens/index.html' target='_blank'>http://www.fas.harvard.edu/~planets/sstewart/ahrens/index.html</a> 
			(Item#: 179 - Parts <a href='http://www.fas.harvard.edu/~planets/sstewart/ahrens/Papers_pdf/Seismo_1396p1.pdf' target='_blank'>1</a> 
